man hasil Tes Kesehatan Halaman 2\"]<a rel=\"attachment wp-att-327\" href=\"https://poliakamigasplg.ac.id/site/?attachment_id=327\"><img class=\"size-full wp-image-327   \" title=\"Pengumuman Hasil Tes Kesehatan \" src=\"https://poliakamigasplg.ac.id/uploads/2011/06/TK21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"459\" height=\"756\" /></a>[/caption]\n\n&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;', 0, 'admin', '127.0.0.1', '2011-06-18 12:49:31', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'y');
